# QA and Commit Gates

- After implementation, run `npm run lint` and `npm run build` unless explicitly skipped.
- For UI changes, include manual mobile QA notes.
- For geo/map/auth/join-flow changes, include regression risks.
- Report changed files.
- Report verification results.
- Provide a concise git commit command.
- Do not claim checks passed unless they actually ran.
